text: a l laoh chea anak del ban bangkeut mekh teang brapir chean ning phendei ka dauchaknea der . batobanhchea( robsa a l laoh) trauv ke banhchouh mk rveang vea teangpir(mekh ning phendei) daembi aoy puok anakdoeng tha pit brakd nasa a l laoh mean anoupheap leu avei teangoasa haey pit brakd nasa a l laoh doeng chruotachreab leu avei teangoasa
